{"tid":141170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係果欄做左年半，你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-02T16:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T16:15:16.000Z","uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff50ae0b7455574bc04985084786051b65b6794c","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如題"},{"pid":"cd5bfbde4673ed34283aeb2b362a64fedd68db39","tid":141170,"uid":56516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"你日日既lunch係咪都諗緊食咩生果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2938f3ef9618533c4f653217231b04e8989fe5","tid":141170,"uid":68610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"好似好雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇黑社會"},{"pid":"23f9aa8421c5641078ca7c1f0e2313cafb80086c","tid":141170,"uid":54095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如題</blockquote><br />\n夜晚果欄d 貨車同幾十板生果 永遠單線行車<br />\n從來無猶差趕 係未有特權？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 呢幾年買生果買到上晒癮 d 日系生果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連車厘都要食塔斯"},{"pid":"638325da9d47690093bf8e522972d31f73d622cd","tid":141170,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如題</blockquote><br />\n夜晚果欄d 貨車同幾十板生果 永遠單線行車<br />\n從來無猶差趕 係未有特權？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 呢幾年買生果買到上晒癮 d 日系生果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連車厘都要食塔斯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晚晚要經個條路拎車都要一眼關七，又要避馬路車又要避拉生果車，仲要比生果佬仇視阻住佢地返工咁"},{"pid":"c26af000aa3a3fcc81a76f08295034945c364363","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如題</blockquote><br />\n夜晚果欄d 貨車同幾十板生果 永遠單線行車<br />\n從來無猶差趕 係未有特權？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 呢幾年買生果買到上晒癮 d 日系生果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連車厘都要食塔斯</blockquote><br />\n 啦有無特權呢依家野我真係唔知，只不過果欄真係百幾年都係咁"},{"pid":"537e3952fbf1de25ed5f0e15f193864ad5d25b10","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你日日既lunch係咪都諗緊食咩生果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b48b15d3cde9c138ea9a2607a1cce20c748a59","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇黑社會</blockquote><br />\n度度都有㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db70e393abb0b5741b7110a2a2ea2b01d2ae21df","tid":141170,"uid":47591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"巴打我想搵批發拎貨擺門市做零售，有冇介紹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d952739421b20e83edaa13324d215760be5614","tid":141170,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"請唔請part time做野？"},{"pid":"c0f870d692b72293e2029bbda957ba35625ce482","tid":141170,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"返工時間係點<br />\n<br />\n幾錢人工<br />\n<br />\n負責做咩"},{"pid":"7904d3d79f4d56747ca12eaa70d52abbd2e30253","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我想搵批發拎貨擺門市做零售，有冇介紹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你夜晚黎睇下，有咩啱買返去鋪頭就得咖啦<br />\n再唔係宜家日頭都好多有貨買㗎，有啲重平過夜晚"},{"pid":"62b796d343af3057588b388ca667ade317876d42","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔請part time做野？</blockquote><br />\n你去搵下咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bfa1d15811536a6e2aa415eecc35dce184e982","tid":141170,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"點入行，係咪要有uncle daddy帶住先做得"},{"pid":"7a983ac3dc7243cdabeebef91816cd02a6cd2882","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工時間係點<br />\n<br />\n幾錢人工<br />\n<br />\n負責做咩</blockquote><br />\n其實我就做日間嘅，夜晚批發就小好多<br />\n人工嘅話 間間唔同<br />\n我就賣野嘅"},{"pid":"db9b364b456ffa3befe71a98438c2f98899b4b94","tid":141170,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"琼姐正唔正？"},{"pid":"3349627ee679bd3f417e57e83a8a7c6d5409a2c0","tid":141170,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"見過有一檔 <br />\n近馬路係門口<br />\n條友換d唔知邊到黎既士多啤梨<br />\n入去日本士多啤梨包裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c620231482051b1ad777d6245027f4ae7f03150c","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過有一檔 <br />\n近馬路係門口<br />\n條友換d唔知邊到黎既士多啤梨<br />\n入去日本士多啤梨包裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家啲日本士多啤梨有部分一到香港就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲貨唔靚，無理由掉左佢㗎<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲行家就會自己check返啲貨<br />\n執返靚仔，唔靚嘅會唔要<br />\n<br />\n你可以放心，無人會用其他地方嘅士多啤梨換做日本嘅，因為一入口你就知㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢地係有責任心先咁做，有啲行家唔理有無爛都照賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fc42335ca11ec2cb44f1211a312e67149938ab","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琼姐正唔正？</blockquote><br />\n自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a1441c5944ce4a60eda6117b39650f66c7420f","tid":141170,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:05:07.000Z","msg":"係咪會平過出面？<br />\n揸車黎有無位泊？<br />\n<br />\n未去過 想去買生果"},{"pid":"b94d9f6e8fc49568ee22c6cbacedf67f30fb5377","tid":141170,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪會平過出面？<br />\n揸車黎有無位泊？<br />\n<br />\n未去過 想去買生果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部分都會平啲<br />\n泊車要自己搵下啦<br />\n依排差人趕車都趕得幾勁下"}]}